pandas2.2.1
Python's version of Excel, but in code. Reads CSV files, cleans missing values, filters rows, groups by category. You need this just to open the Kaggle training data files.
In your app: df = pd.read_csv("ieee_fraud.csv") → df.fillna(0) → ready to train

